name: Attack Scenario
description: Attack Scenario is Recordtype for Scenario Objecttype. An Attack Scenario is root element of Attack Tree

name: Attack:Goal
description: An Attack:GOal  is Recordtype for Objecttype Pathway.  An Attack Goal  is the  root element of Attack Tree

name: Attack:Method
description: An Attack Method  is Recordtype for Objecttype Pathway.  An Attack Method is sub-node element of an Attack Vector

name: Attack:Vector
description: An Attack Vector is Recordtype for Objecttype Pathway.  An Attack Vector is a node element of Attack Tree

name: Counter Measure
description: Counter Measures are applicable to Attack Methods
